{"tid":1490541,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Edifier S350DB VGA 延長線","createTime":"2019-08-20T06:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T23:18:00.000Z","uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"548b5053b85043c2111186f32072b1a30510e7cc","tid":1490541,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"話說小弟早排買左部s350db <br />\n右邊喇叭果條線好長<br />\n但左邊果個就好短 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條線既插頭樣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phtvQfw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FphtvQfw.png&h=785da95a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我買左條線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YsLumnF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYsLumnF.png&h=4316820d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為我唔識 所以淨係拎左上面果張圖去問d 影音鋪<br />\n個老細話一定得 點知番去到插左 部野著唔到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為平時都要用遙控開左佢有燈先會有聲<br />\n<br />\n好似感： 會著左pc 兩個字<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rdRxi9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrdRxi9N.jpg&h=97238d31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n插左果條線雖然開唔到機 但個喇叭都會出到聲 <br />\n但就好細聲 同d聲好似隔左一層野感<br />\n<br />\n想問下有無一條延長線係真係work 既？<br />\n最好有埋個包裝個樣 或者果條線正確既名 我好搵d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ad5f75415c53398b79606a827593d8d27bbd1a","tid":1490541,"uid":153662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:31:49.000Z","msg":"我都用350DB但幫唔到你<br />\n幫推ONLY"},{"pid":"68189b4201e2e8e9610b5e1b4bc9552ed586110b","tid":1490541,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44ad5f75415c53398b79606a827593d8d27bbd1a","tid":1490541,"uid":153662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:31:49.000Z","msg":"我都用350DB但幫唔到你<br />\n幫推ONLY"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d71bcdea84e7a132bf1000ff720cbe5e945e497","tid":1490541,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}